enum TeamType {
    HOME = "HOME",
    AWAY = "AWAY"
}
enum StatType {
    twoPointsMade = "twoPointsMade",
    twoPointsMissed = "twoPointsMissed",
    threePointsMade = "threePointsMade",

    oRebounds = "oRebounds",
    dRebounds = "dRebounds",
    assists = "assists",
    steals = "steals",
    blocks = "blocks",
    turnovers = "turnovers",
}


export { TeamType, StatType };
